<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9206001002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure, noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Install headlight unit clip (1).
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Install headlight unit bolts (2) in numerical order (“1” – “4”).
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
The headlight unit bolts are precoated with friction stabilizer. If these bolts are reused, they may work loose.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to replace the headlight unit bolts with new ones whenever they are removed.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A920005.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "68.998mm" ver = "02" gw = "219" gh = "179"/>
</figure>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
